name: TheNextWebNews
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, what's in the news?”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: After enabling The Next Web News skill on your device, you can use commands like “Alexa, what’s my flash briefing” or “Alexa, what’s in the news” to hear your flash briefing from The Next Web News latest feed. If you would like to hear the news from this skill before other flash brief skills, move it to the top from your news brief settings. Excellent everyday assistant for tech enthusiasts.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
